edu.nd.darts.cimon
Class MetricNodes

java.lang.Object
  edu.nd.darts.cimon.MetricNodes
Deprecated. 

public final class MetricNodes
extends Object

Maintains a static list of all currently instantiated metric management nodes. When a call needs to be made to a management node (CurrentNode) for a particular metric, this list should be referenced first to determine if an instance of that node already exist. If not, a new node may be instantiated and added to this list. This is to ensure there is only one active management node for each metric.
